title: #327: Cappereira (Nick Capper)
itunes:title: Cappereira with Nick Capper
description: @CapperFlapper had me over to his apartment in Melbourne to talk about travel, farming, his deep sexual love affair with aboriginal history, and shitting. It was an all over the place conversation on one of the most sacred and drunk holidays in Australia, ANZAC Day.
